SETUP
#################
1) the app is in diabetesprediction folder || the preprocessing,diabetes.csv and test.predict are just to preprocess and test models
2) Go to azure portal
3) Go to create web app
4) Make resource group
5) Make name and python run stack
6) change size and sku select free
7) in deploment tab enable continuous deployment 
8) Put file in your gitub in new repository (make sure you have your requirements.txt)
9) in depoyment tab select your github account and repository (main branch)
10) In skip monitor and tags tab then hit review and create
11) in configuration  in setupcommand  do (gunicorn --bind=0.0.0.0 --timeout 600 app:app)
12) go to deployment center and hit sync to redeploy 


